		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In some of their games, such as Castlevania I and II, Konami managed to get some "high priority" sprites with fixed slot (including the hero sometimes) while the enemies, bullets, etc... appear in a lower priority in a pseudo-random order.
<br />So I guess it's the same with this game.

		

